{
  "stem": "14251.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And during those holidays, those few days of leave he had, he took us to the church.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And my mother had already taught me you're not supposed to be comfortable singing some Christmas song or thing.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It's not our song.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But we went to the church, and the pastor or minister there spoke to the teeny, little congregation there on Christmas and to us, as if he knew about us.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And that scared my mother so terribly that we had to get out of there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But he didn't say anything disparaging.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He was trying to tell us that everything-- not everyone is doing what's happening out there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "He was really trying to give encouragement.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I think my mother once said Jehovah's Witnesses came to their door like that, too, and they were scared they were being arrested.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It was Jehovah's Witnesses saying-- taking a chance on their lives.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We've been big fans of Jehovah's Witnesses ever since.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[DRINKS] But we stayed there together.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Except the Nazi woman proved a problem.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "She had two little girls.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And the two little girls were-- one was, I think, a year older than I.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "The other one about three years old.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "The three-year-old one had black hair and black eyes, the epitome of what the Hitler regime would have called a very Jewish-looking child.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "In fact, in our little photograph, she's the only one who looks like a Jewish little child, which is so funny.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "But it wasn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "During play, my mother would sit and knit with this woman.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "She couldn't get rid of this woman.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "The mother of these children would badger and look for her, badger her to come sit with her, because you're the only intelligent person to talk to here.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And I have a degree in racial studies.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
